      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-maintained and runs like a dream! Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, with just a little bit of character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed. Come take it for a spin; I know you'll fall in love with how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
