    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is an E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six power unit. This high-revving engine maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the double VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure precise valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shift throws, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary structural weak point. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and OEM dampers for a compliant yet communicative ride, while the braking system features braided stainless lines for improved pedal modulation. While the finish shows minor road wear, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain alignment remain dialed for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
