    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in wonderful condition for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor cosmetic character marks one would expect from a well-loved but carefully driven car. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and inviting; the premium leather upholstery remains supple, the carpets are free of stains, and the dashboard is pristine. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust and dependable. It has a complete service history, showcasing regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. On the road, it delivers a smooth, quiet ride with precise handling and confident braking. This is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that perfectly balances sophisticated style with everyday practicality. Non-smoker owned and always garage-kept.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
